attachments.title: The Birth of a Nation: The Inspired By Album by Various Artists on Apple Music
attachments.text: Listen to songs from the album The Birth of a Nation: The Inspired By Album, including "Go Tell 'Em," "Black Moses (feat. Priscilla Renea)," "Whip & a Chain," and many more. Buy the album for $10.99. Songs start at $1.29. Free with Apple Music subscription.
